ttp://www.divergentfans.com/profiles/blogs/veronica-roth-and-lionsgate-movie-studio-respond-to-theo-james-ca|title=Veronica Roth and Lionsgate Movie Studio Respond to Theo James Casting in The Divergent Movie|accessdate=2013-06-08|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130511183826/http://www.divergentfans.com/profiles/blogs/veronica-roth-and-lionsgate-movie-studio-respond-to-theo-james-ca|archivedate=2013-05-11}}</ref>”

