Daily News (New York)|accessdate=2013-06-08|archive-date=2020-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200928161526/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/kate-winslet-cast-young-adult-film-divergent-article-1.1295922|dead-url=no}}</ref>。谈到第一次出演反派，温丝莱特表示：“我不傻。这个想法曾从我的头脑闪过，之前我从未演过坏人，我都觉得有点意外。”由于她参加拍摄非常的晚，拍戏第一天，她和其他演员之间距离似乎让她被疏离：“我想要打破僵局，想着‘没事的。我很有趣。我确信。’但想想，就为了今天，我让他们觉得我完全是个婊子<ref name="z">{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/07/16/divergent-kate-winslet-pregnant/2507183/|title=On set of 'Divergent,' Kate Winslet is pregnant and mean|accessdate=2013-06-08|work=USA Today|first1=Bryan|last1=Alexander|archive-date=2015-04-09|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6XesvVjIc?url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/07/16/divergent-kate-winslet-pregnant/2507183/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”当时，温丝莱特已怀孕五个月，她使出各种花招掩盖她的孕味。伯格说：“我们拍她的时非常讲究策略。她总是把某种文件或档案握在手中，算是保护吧，你懂的，她大着肚子<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.yahoo.com/movies/revealed-how-kate-winslet-concealed-her-pregnancy-92087306107.html |title= Revealed: How Kate Winslet Concealed Her Pregnancy While Filming 'Divergent' |accessdate= 2014-08-30 |archive-date= 2016-03-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160305140241/https://www.yahoo.com/movies/revealed-how-kate-winslet-concealed-her-pregnancy-92087306107.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。”2013年3月25日，{{le|本·兰波|Ben Lamb}}出演爱华德，[[本·劳埃德·休斯|本·劳埃德·休斯]]出演威尔，{{le|克里斯蒂安·曼德森|Chrisitian Madsen}}出演艾尔。2013年4月，[[艾什莉·贾德|艾什莉·贾德]]和[[托尼·戈德温|托尼·戈德温]]加盟剧组，出演翠丝的父母娜塔莉和安德鲁<ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/13/divergent-ashley-judd-cast/|title='Divergent': Ashley Judd cast as Natalie Prior|accessdate=2017-05-20|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110175903/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/13/divergent-ashley-judd-cast/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/15/tony-goldwyn-joins-divergent/|title=Tony Goldwyn joins 'Divergent'—Exclusive|accessdate=2017-05-20|archive-date=2014-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110181407/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2013/04/15/tony-goldwyn-joins-divergent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

