chive-date=2014-03-24|archive-url=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20140324093049/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2013-06-23/entertainment/ct-ent-0624-luis-20130623_1_veronica-roth-transformers-divergent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“选派典礼”取景于芝加哥市区东瓦克（{{lang|en|East Wacker}}）{{le|芝加哥科学家第十七基督教堂|Seventeenth Church of Christ, Scientist}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedivergent.net/index.php/87-divergent-film/402-new-filming-location|title=NEW Filming Location!|accessdate=2013-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213220948/http://www.thedivergent.net/index.php/87-divergent-film/402-new-filming-location|archivedate=2013-12-13}}</ref>，外景取景于{{le|先驱教堂|Pioneer Court}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2014-03-06/entertainment/chi-divergent-shailene-woodley-ferris-wheel-20140306_1_ansel-elgort-shailene-woodley-theo-james|title='Divergent' stars talk Rahm Emanuel, Blackhawks and riding the 'L'|work=Chicago Tribune|date=2014-03-06|author=Gomez, Luis|accessdate=2014-09-14|archive-date=2014-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140915025701/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/2014-03-06/entertainment/chi-divergent-shailene-woodley-ferris-wheel-20140306_1_ansel-elgort-shailene-woodley-theo-james|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。影片还在[[海军码头|海军码头]]摩天轮取景，整个地区尘土飞扬，更能体现[[反乌托邦|反乌托邦]]感<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pagetopremiere.com/2013/04/divergent-set-photos-ferris-wheel-scene-being-filmed-on-navy-pier/|title='Divergent' movie set photos: Hugely anticipated ferris wheel scene being filmed on Navy Pier|accessdate=2013-07-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130711040156/http://pagetopremiere.com/2013/04/divergent-set-photos-ferris-wheel-scene-being-filmed-on-navy-pier/|archivedate=2013-07-11}}</ref>。取景地还包括[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]附近的第57大街和埃利斯大道<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/06/14/divergent-filming-around-the-university-of-chicago-this-weekend/|title='Divergent' filming around the University of Chicago & 600 S Wells St this weekend|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811100514/https://onlocationvacations.com/2013/06/14/divergent-filming-around-the-university-of-chicago-this-weekend/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、联邦街（搭建了假的[[芝加哥地铁|芝加哥地铁]]）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/05/26/new-photos-and-videos-of-divergent-filming-in-chicago-this-weekend/|title=New photos and videos of 'Divergent' filming in Chicago this weekend!|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811102117/https://onlocationvacations.com/2013/05/26/new-photos-and-videos-of-divergent-filming-in-chicago-this-weekend/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[密歇根大街_(芝加哥)|密歇根大街]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2013/05/23/new-divergent-filming-locations-spotted-in-chicago-for-may-24-2013/|title=Upadte New 'Divergent' filming locations spotted in Chicago for May 24, 2013|accessdate=2013-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811102000/https://onlocationvacations.com/2013/05/23/new-divergent-filming-locations-spotted-in-chicago-for-may-24-2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。芝加哥大学的{{le|乔和丽卡曼苏托图书馆|Joe and Rika Mansueto Library}}也是取景地<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://news.uchicago.edu/article/2014/03/14/students-learn-about-feature-filmmaking-divergent-internships|title = Students learn about feature filmmaking with 'Divergent' internships|date = 2014-03-14|accessdate = 2015-03-22|website = UChicagoNews|publisher = The University of Chicago|last = Douglass|first = Dianna|archive-date = 2018-03-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180307151036/https://news.uchicago.edu/article/2014/03/14/students-learn-about-feature-filmmaking-divergent-internships|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

