=== 评价 ===
《分歧者》收穫了兩極的評價。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的203篇專業影評文章，其中83篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為41%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]5.4分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/divergent/|title = Divergent (2014)|publisher = {{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}}|work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate = May 2, 2014|archive-date = 2020-11-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130144117/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/divergent|dead-url = no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的38篇評論文章，其中12篇予以好評，2篇差評，24篇褒貶不一，平均分為48（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.metacritic.com/movie/divergent| title = Divergent: Reviews (2014)| publisher = [[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]| work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]]| accessdate = March 17, 2014| archive-date = 2020-11-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127015247/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/divergent| dead-url = no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾比影評人更能接受這部電影，給予評價「A」，而該調查組中有69%是女性，且一半的觀眾超過25歲<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-divergent-breaks-ya-690460 | work=The Hollywood Reporter | first=Pamela | last=McClintock | title=Box Office: 'Divergent' Breaks YA Curse With $56 Million Debut; 'Muppets 2' Bombs | date=March 23, 2014 | accessdate=2016-12-12 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022852/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-divergent-breaks-ya-690460 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.thewrap.com/divergent-box-office-shailene-woodley-theo-james-franchise-born |title= ‘Divergent’ Scores $56 Million Box-Office Opening, ‘A’ CinemaScore – And a Franchise Is Born (Video) |accessdate= March 24, 2014 |archive-date= 2014-03-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140326163957/http://www.thewrap.com/divergent-box-office-shailene-woodley-theo-james-franchise-born |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

