== 續集 ==
2013年5月7日，顶峰娱乐透露改编自《[[反叛者_(小说)|反叛者]]》的续集正在创作中。《{{le|拿起枪的简|Jane Got a Gun}}》编剧布莱恩·杜菲尔德（{{lang|en|Brian Duffield}}）受聘撰写剧本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/divergent-sequel-insurgent-brian-duffield/|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|title=Summit Sets Brian Duffield to Pen DIVERGENT Sequel, INSURGENT|publisher=Collider.com|date=2013-05-07|accessdate=2013-05-08|archive-date=2015-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150726110607/http://collider.com/divergent-sequel-insurgent-brian-duffield/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。续集于2015年3月20日上映。第三部作品改编自小说《{{le|赤诚者|Allegiant (novel)}}》起初被宣布作为单部电影，定于2016年3月18日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/gods-of-egypt-release-date/|last=Trumbore|first=Dave|title=Summit Sets Release Dates for Divergent Threequel Allegiant, Plus Gods of Egypt and Step Up All In|publisher=Collider.com|date=2013-12-16|accessdate=2013-12-17|archive-date=2015-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002143903/http://collider.com/gods-of-egypt-release-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hypable.com/2013/12/16/allegiant-movie-release-date/|last=Sims|first=Andrew|title=Summit sets March 2016 date for ‘Allegiant,’ avoids a split (for now)|publisher=hypable.com|date=2013-12-16|accessdate=2014-01-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106032258/http://www.hypable.com/2013/12/16/allegiant-movie-release-date/|archivedate=2014-01-06}}</ref>。2013年12月，尼尔·伯格宣布不会回归执导续集，由于他正在创作第一部电影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/divergent-director-neil-burger-wont-do-sequel-exclusive-1200966623/|title=‘Divergent’ Director Neil Burger Won’t Do Sequel but he will be co producer of insurgent and helping out (Exclusive)|accessdate=2013-12-17|work=Variety|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121054318/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/divergent-director-neil-burger-wont-do-sequel-exclusive-1200966623/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年2月11日，[[罗伯特·斯文克|罗伯特·斯文克]]宣布接替伯格导演续集<ref>{{cite news|url=http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/divergent-sequel-insurgent-finds-director-in-robert-schwentke/#/0|title=Divergent’ sequel ‘Insurgent’ finds director in Robert Schwentke|publisher=herocomplex.latimes.com|date=2014-02-23|accessdate=2014-02-11|archive-date=2018-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904191915/http://herocomplex.latimes.com/movies/divergent-sequel-insurgent-finds-director-in-robert-schwentke/#/0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/robert-schwentke-insurgent-director-divergent-sequel/|title=Robert Schwentke To Direct ‘Divergent’ Sequel ‘Insurgent’|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-02-11|author=Fleming Jr, Mike|accessdate=2017-05-21|archive-date=2014-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512192259/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/robert-schwentke-insurgent-director-divergent-sequel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。续集于2014年5月27日在亚特兰大开机拍摄<ref>{{cite web|title=‘Divergent’ Sequel ‘Insurgent’ Starts Filming in Atlanta May 27th!|url=http://www.fanbolt.com/divergent-sequel-insurgent-starts-filming-atlanta-may-27th/|accessdate=2014-04-27|archive-date=2014-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426234416/http://www.fanbolt.com/divergent-sequel-insurgent-starts-filming-atlanta-may-27th/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年9月6日杀青<ref>{{cite web|title='Insurgent' Movie News: Cast Wraps Up Production In Atlanta, Could See A Little More Filming With Trailer Coming In November [VIDEO]|url=http://www.enstarz.com/articles/46103/20140912/insurgent-movie-news-cast-wraps-up-production-in-atlanta-could-see-a-little-more-filming-with-trailer-coming-in-november-video.htm|accessdate=2014-09-14|archive-date=2015-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151121095439/http://www.enstarz.com/articles/46103/20140912/insurgent-movie-news-cast-wraps-up-production-in-atlanta-could-see-a-little-more-filming-with-trailer-coming-in-november-video.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年4月11日，顶峰娱乐宣布第三部分拆为上下集，上集于2016年3月18日上映，下集于2017年6月9日上映<ref>{{cite news | title=Lionsgate Splitting Third ‘Divergent’ Book ‘Allegiant’ into Two Films | url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/lionsgate-splitting-third-divergent-book-allegiant-into-two-films-1201155988/ | work=Variety | accessdate=2017-05-21 | archive-date=2014-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219105645/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/lionsgate-splitting-third-divergent-book-allegiant-into-two-films-1201155988/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="move back">{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-divergent-movie-shailene-woodley-1201664379/|title=‘Power Rangers,’ Final ‘Divergent’ Movie’s Release Dates Moved Back|last=McNary|first=Dave|work=Variety|date=2015-12-17|accessdate=2015-12-19|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307010435/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/power-rangers-divergent-movie-shailene-woodley-1201664379/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月5日，斯文克表示会执导上集<ref>{{cite news | title=‘Insurgent’ Director Robert Schwentke Returning for ‘Allegiant Part 1′ (EXCLUSIVE) | url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/insurgent-director-robert-schwentke-returning-for-allegiant-part-1-exclusive-1201372155/ | work=Variety | accessdate=2017-05-21 | archive-date=2020-10-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026223553/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/insurgent-director-robert-schwentke-returning-for-allegiant-part-1-exclusive-1201372155/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年9月10日，两部电影改名，上集改称《[[分歧者3：忠诚世界|分歧者3：忠诚世界]]》，下集改称《[[分歧者4：上升之势|分歧者4：上升之势]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/final-two-divergent-films-get-821813|title=Final Two 'Divergent' Films Get New Titles, Logos|author=Mia Galuppo|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=([[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]])|date=2015-09-10|accessdate=2015-09-11|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107052518/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/final-two-divergent-films-get-821813|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年2月8日，斯文克宣布不会执导结局篇<ref>{{cite web | url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/robert-schwentke-divergent-ascendant-shailene-woodley-theo-james-1201698820/ | title=Robert Schwentke Exits ‘Divergent’ Finale ‘Ascendant’ | work=Deadline | date=2016-02-08 | accessdate=2016-02-09 | author=Flemming, Mike | archive-date=2020-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201043354/https://deadline.com/2016/02/robert-schwentke-divergent-ascendant-shailene-woodley-theo-james-1201698820/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，{{le|李·托兰德·克莱格|Lee Toland Krieger}}接替他<ref>{{cite web|title=Ascendant Lands Age of Adaline’s Lee Toland Krieger to Direct Divergent Finale|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/661757-ascendant-lands-age-of-adalines-lee-toland-krieger-to-direct-divergent-finale#/slide/1|accessdate=2016-03-16|archive-date=2018-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222044026/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/661757-ascendant-lands-age-of-adalines-lee-toland-krieger-to-direct-divergent-finale#/slide/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

